%b.icon-info-sign
  Help
%p
  This is a page for one of your tours. On this page you can:
%ul
  %li
    =link_to "Manage bookings for this tour", "#", :data => {:scroll => "#calendar"}
  %li
    =link_to("Add a new tour", new_performer_tour_path(tour.performer))
  %li
    -if tour.performer.tours
      =link_to("Edit all your tours", performer_tours_path(tour.performer)+"#all" )
%p
  Alternatively you could:   
%ul
  %li
    =link_to "Post an update on your wall", performer_path(tour.performer) + "#wall"
  %li
    =link_to "View all other performers", performers_path 